{"tid":2365820,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Galaxy S21 發佈會   首度通過抖音直播","createTime":"2021-01-14T05:08:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T02:24:35.000Z","uid":58335,"like":5,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e9f167d60b06b43c305e573678f0751692b401e2","tid":2365820,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T05:08:25.000Z","msg":"抖陰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚（1 月 14 日）是 Galaxy S21 系列、Galaxy Buds Pro 和 Galaxy SmartTag 發佈的大日子，如果你打算今晚收看 Galaxy Unpacked 發佈會，Samsung 將會提供多個渠道，除了一直使用的官方 YouTube 頻道，還有 3 個新的平台會同步直播。<br />\n<br />\nSamsung 昨日宣佈會首次通過 TikTok、Twitch 和 Reddit，串流直播 Galaxy Unpacked 發佈會，發佈會將會在香港時間晚上 11 時開始，想知道 Galaxy S21 系列手機，還有 Galaxy Buds Pro 藍牙耳機和 Galaxy SmartTag 追蹤配件的詳細資料，屆時可以留意我們的更新。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：androidpolice<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4523/217556/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4523%2F217556%2F1%2F&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuOxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=9e27b878\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4523/217556/1/</a>"},{"pid":"5bda9ef6e0d6840c606fb10b9f7f5d6f7c7973cc","tid":2365820,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T05:50:16.000Z","msg":"笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8711eaf4fefead9f1fc7121cbcd48f9e5a6b9a3e","tid":2365820,"uid":47643,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:15:12.000Z","msg":"好心就學下小米la"},{"pid":"6fe235d38c82edd50517cb123de3e24046a94407","tid":2365820,"uid":180173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:15:55.000Z","msg":"抖陰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2b77dad753c7031b93029634a9b2aefd5fc16b8","tid":23658